        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="fWfy_zopAMzZ9MZUP1sN-51" parent="1" style="whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;sketch=1;hachureGap=4;jiggle=2;curveFitting=1;fontFamily=Architects Daughter;fontSource=https%3A%2F%2Ffonts.googleapis.com%2Fcss%3Ffamily%3DArchitects%2BDaughter;" value="4" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="49" width="53" x="-443" y="1758" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="-Z2AB0EwvTVkitUTac_q-1" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;fontSize=20;fontFamily=Architects Daughter;fontSource=https%3A%2F%2Ffonts.googleapis.com%2Fcss%3Ffamily%3DArchitects%2BDaughter;" value="RLHF而言：&lt;div&gt;1、训练时间成本高，需要先训练奖励模型，再训练最终的模型（策略模型）&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;2、显存占用高：训练策略模型的时候&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;需要在显存当中加载3个模型：&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;-- 1️⃣、sft之后的模型，用做参考模型：它的作用就是在PPO训练过程当中，防止训练之后的模型和原模型偏离太远&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;2️⃣、奖励模型：用来对策略模型自回归生成的结果，进行打分&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;3️⃣、策略模型：实际需要更新参数的策略模型&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;3、训练不稳定，训练难度高，对于超参数，极为敏感&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="30" width="745" x="17.5" y="1311" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="-Z2AB0EwvTVkitUTac_q-2" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;fontSize=20;fontFamily=Architects Daughter;fontSource=https%3A%2F%2Ffonts.googleapis.com%2Fcss%3Ffamily%3DArchitects%2BDaughter;" value="SFT:&lt;div&gt;计算batch当中所有token的平均损失&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="30" width="383" x="104" y="1657" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="-Z2AB0EwvTVkitUTac_q-4" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;fontSize=20;fontFamily=Architects Daughter;fontSource=https%3A%2F%2Ffonts.googleapis.com%2Fcss%3Ffamily%3DArchitects%2BDaughter;" value="DPO:&lt;div&gt;1、基于一个prompt的chose数据，需要先通过需要训练模型前向传播，得到\pi_(y_w | x)&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;2、基于一个prompt的rejected数据，需要通过需要的模型，前向传播，&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;\pi_(y_l | x)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;3、&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;基于一个prompt的chose数据，需要经过参考模型\pi_{ref} (y_w | x)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;4、&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;基于一个prompt的rejected数据，需要经过参考模型\pi_{ref} (y_l | x)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;5、计算最终损失：&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;-log \sigmoid (\beta [&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;\pi_(log(y_w | x) -log(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;\pi_(y_l | x)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;) - (log(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;\pi_{ref} (y_w | x)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;)) - log(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;\pi_{ref} (y_l | x)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;))&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;])&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="30" width="383" x="64.5" y="1935.5" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
